threats.title: Man in the Middle
threats.description: The AI could intercept the database queries in transit and obtain sensitive information, such as credentials, query parameters or query results.
threats.mitigation: Enforce an encrypted connection to the web application

threats.title: Man in The Middle Attack
threats.description: The AI could intercept the database queries in transit and obtain sensitive information, such as credentials, query parameters or query results (is unlikely since the data flow is over a private network)
threats.mitigation: Enforce an encrypted connection to the server

threats.title: Unauthorized Access
threats.description: The AI could be able to conduct an query call to the platform database upon gaining enough information via successful MiTM (Man in the middle) attacks
threats.mitigation: Require the authentication to not be outdated and able to detect suspicious request.

threats.title: Credential Theft
threats.description: The AI could obtain the database credentials and use them to make unauthorised queries.
threats.mitigation: Use a firewall to restrict access to the DB to only the Background Worker IP address.

threats.title: Poison messages
threats.description: Automatic generated malicious message(s) made by AI which prevent background worker process.
threats.mitigation: Validate the content of all messages, before processing. Reject any message that have invalid content and log the rejection, do not log the malicious content; instead log a description of the error.
